		<div class="entry-content"><div id="sharetools-story" class="sharetools theme-classic sharetools-story" data-shares="email|Email,facebook|Share,twitter|Tweet,save|Save,show-all|More,ad" data-url="//boss.blogs.nytimes.com/2014/12/17/today-in-small-business-the-years-best-franchises/" data-title="Today in Small Business: The Year&#8217;s Best Franchises" data-description="Can the S.B.A. stay relevant? Will a subscription model work for the movies? Is it acceptable to read and respond to messages during a meeting?">
				<div class="ad sharetools-inline-article-ad"></div>
				<div id="MiddleLeft" class="ad middle-left-ad nocontent robots-nocontent"></div>
				</div><div class="inlineModule"><div class="entry"><h6 class="kicker"><a href="//boss.blogs.nytimes.com/category/dashboard/">Dashboard</a></h6><p class="summary">A daily roundup of small-business developments.</p></div></div>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">Whatâs affecting me, my clients and other small-business owners today.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>The Economy</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><a href="//www.reuters.com/article/2014/12/17/us-usa-economy-idUSKBN0JV1EX20141217">Consumer prices</a> record their biggest drop in nearly six years.</li>
<li>General Electric said it <a href="//www.foxbusiness.com/industries/2014/12/16/ge-expects-2015-industrials-units-profit-to-rise-at-least-10/">expected profit</a> from its industrial units to rise by at least 10 percent in 2015.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Washington</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Here&#8217;s how the Small Business Administration is <a href="//www.washingtonpost.com/business/on-small-business/striving-to-stay-relevant-small-business-administration-evolves-under-new-leader/2014/12/16/59bbd908-8156-11e4-9f38-95a187e4c1f7_story.html">trying to stay relevant</a>.</li>
<li>The spending bill again <a href="https://www.americanexpress.com/us/small-business/openforum/articles/sbas-size-standard-rules-getting-second-look/">raises the issue</a> of whether the S.B.A. is truly focused on <em>small</em> businesses.</li>
<li>This is what it took to <a href="//dealbook.nytimes.com/2014/12/15/in-push-out-provision-example-of-how-congress-does-its-job/">weaken regulation</a> of Wall Street.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Franchising</strong></p>
<ul>
<ul>
<li>Here are the top <a href="//www.entrepreneur.com/slideshow/240719?">10 franchises</a> of 2015, according to Entrepreneur Magazine.</li>
</ul>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><span id="more-90996"></span></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Retail</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Americans like the idea of <a href="//wnpr.org/post/americans-love-local-business-do-they-spend-accordingly#.VJ">shopping locally</a>, but they don&#8217;t actually do it.</li>
<li>Sears <a href="//www.wsj.com/articles/sears-bets-big-on-technology-but-at-the-expense-of-its-stores-1418787001">bets on technology</a> (at expense of its stores).</li>
<li>Does <a href="//eagnews.org/prof-elf-on-the-shelf-conditions-kids-to-accept-surveillance-state/?">Elf on the Shelf</a> set up children for &#8220;dangerous, uncritical acceptance of power structures?â</li>
<li>Researchers say <a href="//www.marketingpilgrim.com/2014/12/can-yelp-reviews-predict-restaurant-closures-researchers-say-yes.html?">Yelp reviews</a> can predict restaurant closings.</li>
<li>This party-game company <a href="//time.com/3634443/cards-against-humanity-poop-black-friday/">sent poop</a> to 30,000 people for Black Friday.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Cash Flow</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>A mobile point-of-sale provider, ShopKeep, <a href="//www.slashgear.com/startup-wants-to-eat-squares-lunch-with-apple-pay-emv-15359492/">wants to challenge</a> Square by offering its payment technology to new customers for free.</li>
<li>Here are 14 things <a href="//dealnews.com/features/more-expensive-in-2015/">that are likely to be more</a> expensive in 2015.</li>
<li>Will <a href="//www.nytimes.com/2014/12/16/business/from-amc-and-moviepass-a-film-a-day-for-a-monthly-fee.html">a subscription model</a> work for the movies? (We <a href="//boss.blogs.nytimes.com/2013/02/13/taking-a-third-pass-at-selling-movie-subscriptions/">wrote about MoviePass</a> in 2013.)</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Taxes</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>The Internal Revenue Service <a href="//theweek.com/speedreads/index/273746/speedreads-irs-returns-womans-lifes-savings-mdash-but-says-they-can-take-it-back-whenever-they-want">returns</a> a woman&#8217;s life&#8217;s savings, but says it can take it back whenever it wants.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Management</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Should a terror threat <a href="//www.nytimes.com/2014/12/17/business/media/sony-weighs-terrorism-threat-against-opening-of-the-interview.html">block the release</a> of &#8220;The Interview&#8221;?</li>
<li>Here&#8217;s what you <a href="//fusefinancialpartners.com/protect-trade-secrets/">need to know</a> to protect trade secrets.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Finance</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Quirky, a product-development company, is <a href="//www.crainsnewyork.com/article/20141212/TECHNOLOGY/141219932">looking to raise</a> $50 million in debt financing.</li>
<li>Bloomberg Philanthropies <a href="//www.bloomberg.org/press/releases/bloomberg-philanthropies-expands-innovation-team-program-12-new-american-cities/">selects</a> 12 cities to participate in its Innovation Teams program.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Health Care</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Nearly 2.5 million people <a href="//www.cnbc.com/id/102273913">have enrolled</a> on Healthcare.gov.</li>
<li>Lots of health insurers have voluntarily <a href="//www.vox.com/2014/12/16/7403619/obamacare-deadline-extension-states">extended their application</a> period into late December.</li>
<li>Here is how small businesses are riding the <a href="//www.cnbc.com/id/102252717">ups and downs</a> of the insurance market.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Around the Country</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>A chief executive program in Indiana aims <a href="//www.wsbt.com/news/local/ceo-program-to-encourage-local-teens-to-become-entrepreneurs/30241228">to encourage</a> teenagers to become entrepreneurs.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Around the World</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>The <a href="//www.nytimes.com/2014/12/17/business/international/slowdown-in-china-bruises-economy-in-latin-america.html">slowdown in China</a> is having an impact on Latin America.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Social Media</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>A social media manager explains why businesses <a href="//www.dexmedia.com/blog/business-needs-use-social-media-customer-service/">need to use</a> social media for customer service.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Online</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>A <a href="//now.avg.com/is-lack-of-trust-limiting-the-potential-for-new-online-services/?u">lack of trust</a> may be limiting the potential for new online services.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Employees</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Former employees have filed a <a href="//www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/employees-file-class-action-lawsuit-sony-article-1.2047356">class-action lawsuit</a> against Sony over the recent hacking scandal.</li>
<li>ZenPayroll helps employers <a href="//venturebeat.com/2014/12/16/zenpayroll-now-lets-companies-match-employees-charitable-donations/">match their employeesâ charitable donations</a>.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Ideas</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>These hired elves <a href="//www.detroitnews.com/story/business/2014/12/15/holiday-help/20466281/">take the stress</a> out of Christmas for their customers.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Opportunities</strong></p>
<ul>
