<li>Uber&#8217;s valuation has investors in a frenzy to <a href="//dealbook.nytimes.com/2014/12/16/throwing-money-at-start-ups-in-frenzy-to-find-the-next-uber/">throw money at start-ups</a>.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Technology</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>The Google Maps team has <a href="//www.pcworld.com/article/2860099/google-maps-9-2-adds-navigation-voice-controls-calibration-tool.html#tk.rss_all">issued</a> another update.</li>
<li>An online human resources software service is fighting a Utah Insurance Department ruling to <a href="//techcrunch.com/2014/12/16/zenefits-fires-back-at-utah/">stop offering</a> free services.</li>
<li>According to a survey, only 6 percent of managers <a href="//www.wdtv.com/wdtv.cfm?func=view&amp;section=5-News&amp;item=Smartphones-and-Business-Meetings-Dont-Mix-20046">say it&#8217;s acceptable</a> to read and respond to messages during a meeting.</li>
</ul>
